<bibRefCitation id="E1E5D90EBCB56AB99F50BA8EB1F82DF6" author="Manukyan, AR" editor="Lelej, AS" journalOrPublisher="Pt 5. Dalnauka, Vladivostok" pageId="0" pageNumber="45" pagination="718 - 732" refId="B15" refString="Manukyan, AR, 2007. Diplazontinae. In: Lelej, AS, Ed., Neuropteroidea, Mecoptera, Hymenoptera. Pt 5. Dalnauka, Vladivostok: 718 - 732" title="Diplazontinae." volumeTitle="Neuropteroidea, Mecoptera, Hymenoptera." year="2007">Manukyan (2007)</bibRefCitation>
, but no additional specimens were found in this study.
</paragraph>
